{"tid":1332925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美參議員提案倡禁華為買賣美國專利","createTime":"2019-07-19T13:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T04:18:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f94d1abf7dc407fa7cd97b07dc6874c6119577e6","tid":1332925,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"美參議員提案倡禁華為買賣美國專利<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2195320/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88%E5%80%A1%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2195320%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2588%25A9&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV5Fs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=02cef76d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2195320/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88%E5%80%A1%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兩名共和黨參議員提出法案，禁止中國電訊設備商華為購買或出售美國專利。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述法例草案指，這項法案旨在容許聯邦政府能夠阻止被列入政府貿易黑名單的公司，購買、出售或獨家授權在美國註冊的專利。<br />\n<br />\n法案提議人稱，該法案針對華為。<br />\n<br />\n華為批評，草案限制專利擁有者保護知識產權的權利，令全球質疑美國對保護知識產權的決心。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部5月以國家安全為由將其列入實體清單。這份黑名單禁止美國公司在沒有許可證的情況下向華為提供美國技術。據報，華為正向美國電訊商Verizon施壓，要求就超過200項專利繳付專利費，外界視為是報復美國的管制。"},{"pid":"6e3d2ba84212bd6014cfbacd896bfcc0276b1e1f","tid":1332925,"uid":56323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"華為: 禁止美國使用好濛系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7bf541c725d83733fc2244d19899b0451b9ee0","tid":1332925,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"買唔到咪偷囉"}]}